Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.96,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}彼此相望  我此刻起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:35.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与你共赴璀璨的明天
