Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…给很多人添麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你的事  再多加一件可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:01:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去永不凋零的樱花那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  到那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错  都是因为我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大家和哥哥…做了那么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----Staff-----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.93,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕制作：澄空学园 & 雪飘工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.93,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,片源：ayukas    翻譯：桜色の祈り  絕靈之手    校對：七夜雙識    後期：Span  volence  阿爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于下期魔法特辑的封面制作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是时候根据调查内容  把报导具体地整理一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你怎么了  立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你能率直地道歉是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你有什么心事吗  整个人在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我只是有点睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  森园学姐会发呆真是稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说又在想新的设定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那么说会挨骂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  今天的会议就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----Title-----
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:23.62,title,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆和起始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天见过樱之后样子就怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴啊  不过我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是想起来…可能有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是蕴藏在永不凋零的樱花中的记忆流进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以心中充满了很多回忆  让我有点混乱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…小樱也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的森园学姐是怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个样子的立夏姐还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时总是雷厉风行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实并非如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们两个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也会一边说着“好累呀”一边犯懒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  今天看来不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是有那种感觉  但可能是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在这样的大雨中  连伞也不撑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  姬乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果寻求温暖的话  肯定又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害到最喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我专用的入口  他特意没有修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是兄妹  所以不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身这么冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗  随意进入别人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是私闯民宅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  我们只是避避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了会被训斥的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的错  因为我的愿望  让大家受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连最喜欢的哥哥也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以什么都不说就一直在逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  我已经什么都做不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一个被称为“孤高的洋兰”的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是少女时的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  再这么慢吞吞的就不管你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉卡  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在附近休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  正好有个适合休息的树荫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天我原本打算穿越前面的森林  前往下一个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达村子之前  天都要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在森林里露宿可是很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也觉得有点不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  莉卡还是和往常一样随性而为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  能不能再多走走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  前面有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为风很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  这是该笑的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  只是感觉这真像是莉卡的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么  走还是不走？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  走吧  不过只再多走一小段路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是道歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点想感谢我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  如果不是莉卡带我出来旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就看不到这样的景色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然邀请的方法有点强硬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经十年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从莉卡强行把我带出来开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这个说法有点问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也没什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉卡真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说奇怪的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉卡  收下这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是魔法使的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经…是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是喜欢上一个人  要是有了想守护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变得不能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能和你一起继续旅行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是吉尔自己的选择啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我带她出来旅行  她便失去了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她遇到了即使放弃魔法也要去珍视的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向失去魔法的她袭来的是  魔女狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够使用魔法的话  她或许就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就能逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  当我闻讯赶到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我现在就想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉卡  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不好  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我带你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉卡  你能听一下我最后的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么说  不要说什么最后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自一人是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以莉卡  一定不要怨恨别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔  吉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  愿这个世界永远鲜花盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为一个美好的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔  不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我当时没有固执地带她一起旅行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她或许就不会失去魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能早点赶到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能就会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔  自责  停住脚步  逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想起来了  她直到最后依然面带笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…虽然还不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想再逃避了  不想再驻足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一直前进的话  说不定会在某个地方再次见到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经绕了这么久的远路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有这么可爱的女孩子去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会在某个地方等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  和我小时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是时候该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:53.96,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この世界はいつも  移り変わってしまうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:22:01.91,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにボクらが存在コトだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:22:01.91,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs10\pos(130,0)}いる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.60,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}変えようのない１つの現実
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:13.12,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな時代を生き抜いても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:24.45,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにある笑顔をボクは信じていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:31.76,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ  またどこかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.21,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そう願うのは  ボクのワガママ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:41.94,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}会いたいよ  会いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:50.40,EDlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}またその手であたためて欲しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:53.96,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}虽然这个世界总是在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:22:01.91,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}唯独我们所在的此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.60,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}是不容改变的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:13.12,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}无论身处什么时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:24.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的笑容  都是我的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:31.76,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想见你  好想见你  我们何处再会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.21,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这份愿望是我的任性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:41.94,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好想见你  好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:50.40,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好希望你再次用这双手温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个四季如春的小岛上  有一棵巨大的樱花树
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能实现任何愿望  不可思议的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  永不凋零的樱花岛

